    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The engine and transmission are strong, providing a smooth and reliable driving experience that you can depend on for daily use. While the exterior paint retains a nice shine, there are some minor rock chips and light surface scratches consistent with careful regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, though there is some light wear on the driver's seat bolster. All major systems, including the air conditioning and electronics, are fully functional. This is a solid, honest car that offers a great balance of quality and value.",
