    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this reliable and character-filled ride! This car is in fair condition and has been a dependable companion, showing some honest signs of its journey so far. It\u2019s perfect for someone looking for a solid, functional vehicle with plenty of life left at a great value. If you're looking for a practical driver that's ready to go, this is a fantastic opportunity!",
