      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really wonderful shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014perfect for someone who wants a solid, comfy car without any fuss. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road for its next big adventure with you! It drives like a dream and looks fantastic. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
