    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54B32 3.2L straight-six. This high-revving power unit utilizes individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system for optimized torque across the rev range. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential. Crucial preventative maintenance has been performed, including subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS service. The chassis remains taut, supported by MacPherson struts up front and a multi-link rear setup, providing the precise turn-in and feedback enthusiasts demand. A well-maintained driver's car ready for its next stint.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
